<h3>Commentary on "Short Man, Sioux Indian"</h3>
<h4>By Michelle Delaney, Smithsonian Institution</h4>

<audio controls="controls">
<source src="../audio/mp3/wfc.aud.69.236.19.mp3" type="audio/mpeg"/>
<source src="../audio/ogg/wfc.aud.69.236.19.ogg" type="audio/ogg"/> <embed
